project: Welcome to Doodles Journey!       Let's first start off with the basics.                Arrow keys to move, jump, and duck.
Enter the... uh... portal to proceed through each level!
Down arrow to duck.                  finally, try to get to the end and dodge all the enemies!             You have one life, so dont waste it!
Your first enemy! Remember: You have one life!
Spikes! Be careful, they're a 1 hit kill too!
Oh no, so many spikes! Step on the jump pad and then jump to get over!
The jump pad increases your jump strength! But if you touch the Ground, your strength RESETS!
The boss battle is next! Here's a tip: Touch the button!
Dodge the lasers and get past!
Also walk on the speed pad to go faster!
JUMP!!!                 More enemies are coming as well!
Congrats! You've won! I hope it didn't take that long ;)                           Here's a victory cake (that you cant eat)
